{"tid":1699281,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"當某日你死於革命當中而大家只留一句 R.I.P 你點睇","createTime":"2019-11-08T03:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:32:10.000Z","uid":335685,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"87742b011f1b96609460bb19eea0edeed4d87bce","tid":1699281,"uid":335685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"點撚樣安息? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好撚多包袱所以決定等某日被選中, 然後被自殺再係地府收一堆R.I.P, 反正我係覺得天堂我實去唔到亦唔會去, 相對偽善自欺安然等待受苦償還罪過仲活得安樂<br />\n<br />\n我認同實踐一個反抗係需要部署, 需要人脈資金同時間, 大家要記住因為大家係無大台無可能好似政府咁議案出一個戰略而警方進行戰術, 變相大家需要更多自發組織小團體不斷認識同挑選日後同靠既戰友<br />\n而直至真正取得勝果為止我相信無一個時代革命中嘅逝世者會真正安息, 請收起你虛偽嘅R.I.P<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 請銘記每一位已被公布名字嘅義士, 真正做到光復香港之後再好好為每一位義士送上最誠心嘅R.I.P<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 若果一輩子都未能成功你係最需要欠每一位義士一個致歉, 因為係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b42ddade2dcf7e0beef6437f2e813baa239f91d","tid":1699281,"uid":170445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:40:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21e0b1e654daab9fffc5386d87642401c44dfc09","tid":1699281,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxeN9ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxeN9ge.jpg&h=69dfcf07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93d3sB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93d3sB8.jpg&h=cb63a975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足只係condom。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3bb3710e6a73ddd34ce1c57f3db1c29e06d58a","tid":1699281,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f3f1423ff846c4ce7f656486ab24364e6351f3","tid":16